node.text: The happiest of birthdays to my brother & best friend, @seanholladay - The adventures we’ve had and the friendship we’ve forged over the last few years is already worth a lifetime of memories. Without him, this journey wouldn’t even be worth it. Happy Birthday brother! Love ya! Can we break his Instagram today with birthday msgs and a copious amount of 💎 emojis for this gem of a human?
